{"article_id":"e7msNqSwMO2KUHCz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Trump pulls security clearance of ex-CIA Director John Brennan","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"' Mr . Brennan ' s lying and recent conduct","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"characterized by increasingly frenzied commentary","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"is wholly inconsistent with access to the nation ' s most closely held secrets . '","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"President Donald Trump on Wednesday revoked the security clearance of former CIA Director John Brennan ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"who has become a harsh critic of the president ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"and appeared to be targeting others","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"who have disagreed with the administration .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"\" Mr . Brennan ' s lying and recent conduct","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"characterized by increasingly frenzied commentary","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"is wholly inconsistent with access to the nation ' s most closely held secrets and facilities , the very aim of our adversaries","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"which is to sow division and chaos , \"","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders said ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"reading a statement from Trump","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"while briefing reporters on Wednesday .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"\" Mr . Brennan has recently leveraged his status as a former high-ranking official with access to highly sensitive information","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"to make a series of unfounded and outrageous allegations","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"- wild outbursts on the internet and television -","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"about this Administration , \"","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"the president ' s statement continued .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"In addition ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Sanders said ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"the administration is evaluating clearances for former FBI Director James Comey , former Director of National Intelligence James Clapper , former National Security Agency Director Michael Hayden , former national security adviser Susan Rice , former FBI attorney Lisa Page , former Deputy Attorney General Sally Yates , former FBI counterintelligence agent Peter Strzok , former FBI Deputy Director Andrew McCabe ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"whose security clearance was deactivated","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"after he was fired earlier this year ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"and Bruce Ohr ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"who is still in the Justice Department","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"although he was demoted from associate deputy attorney general .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" More broadly , the issue of Mr. Brennan ' s security clearance raises larger questions about the practice of former officials","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"maintaining access to our nation ' s most sensitive secrets","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"long after their time in government has ended , \"","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Sanders said .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"\" This action is part of a broader effort by Mr. Trump","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"to suppress freedom of speech","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"& punish critics , \"","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"he wrote .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"\" It should gravely worry all Americans ,","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"including intelligence professionals ,","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"about the cost","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"of speaking out .","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"My principles are worth far more than clearances .","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"I will not relent , ''","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"he wrote .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"This action is part of a broader effort by Mr. Trump","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"to suppress freedom of speech","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"& punish critics .","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"It should gravely worry all Americans ,","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"including intelligence professionals ,","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"about the cost","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"of speaking out .","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"My principles are worth far more than clearances .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"I will not relent .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"https : //t.co/TNzOxhP9ux","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"- John O. Brennan","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"( @ JohnBrennan )","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"August 15 , 2018","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"In a subsequent phone interview on MSNBC , Brennan added","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"if the president believed","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"that the action would lead the former CIA director \" to just go away and be quiet ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"he is very badly mistaken. \"","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"\" I ' ve seen this type of behavior and actions on the part of foreign tyrants and despots and autocrats during my CIA and national security career , \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"\" I never thought","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"I would see it here in the United States .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"And so I do believe","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"that all Americans really need to take stock of what is happening right now in our government , and how abnormal and how irresponsible and how dangerous these actions are. \"","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Brennan also said","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"he was not informed by the government","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that his security clearance was revoked ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"but instead learned it from a friend","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"who called","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"when Sanders was delivering the president ' s statement .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"The White House last month announced","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that it was looking into revoking security clearances for the individuals","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"Sanders listed ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"with the exception of Yates , Strzok , Page and Ohr ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"whose names were added on Wednesday .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"Trump has over the past couple of days dug into Strzok ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"who was fired from the FBI on Friday ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"and Ohr .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Ohr , a senior Justice Department official , has come under scrutiny","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"after it was revealed he had contact during the 2016 election cycle with Fusion GPS founder Glenn Simpson and former British spy Christopher Steele ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"who compiled a dossier","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"that described a complex conspiracy of Trump and his campaign working with the Kremlin","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"to influence the outcome of the presidential election .","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"Trump has denied the dossier ' s findings .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Ohr 's wife , Nellie , also worked for Fusion GPS during the 2016 election .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"The Justice Department declined to comment on Ohr 's security clearance .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"\" Security clearances for those","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"who still have them","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"may be revoked ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"and those","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"who have already lost their security clearance","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"may not be able to have it reinstated , \"","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Sanders said .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Clapper on Wednesday said during an interview with CNN","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"that he had not had any access to current intelligence","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"since he resigned in January 2017 .","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"Playbook PM","depth":4},{"id":100,"text":"Sign up for our must-read newsletter on what 's driving the afternoon in Washington .","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"By signing up","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"The former intelligence chief has been a harsh critic of Trump","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"and has feuded with the president ,","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"who has characterized the FBI ' s use of an informant as the Justice Department ' s spying on his presidential campaign .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"Clapper , however , has countered","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"that Russian efforts were the subject of intelligence operations , not Trump ' s campaign .","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"Clapper said","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"that losing his clearance wouldn ' t have any \" immediate substantive impact \" on him ,","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"and that he would continue to speak out against the president .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"\" Will the republic stand or fall on whether John retains his access to classified information , or mine or any others","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"that were named ?","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"Of course not , \"","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"\" The larger issue here , to me , throughout has been infringement on First Amendment rights .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"And I think","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"people ought to think seriously about that. \"","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"Comey last month said","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"he no longer had a security clearance ,","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"and Hayden also said on Twitter","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"that he did not go back for classified briefings","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"but would occasionally be asked to \" offer a view on something . \"","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"Comey ,","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"who was fired last year ,","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"documented a conversation with Trump","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"in which he says","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"the president asked him to to let go of an FBI investigation into former Trump campaign adviser Michael Flynn ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"who also served briefly as the president ' s national security adviser .","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"Since the release of Comey ' s memo , special counsel Robert Mueller has broadened his Russia investigation","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"to include","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"whether Trump tried to obstruct justice .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"Trump has long called the Mueller inquiry a \" witch hunt. \"","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"Susan Gordon , principal deputy director of national intelligence , told on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"that she didn ' t know","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"whether the White House consulted National Intelligence Director Dan Coats","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"before it announced the decision","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"to revoke Brennan ' s clearance .","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"\" But it is a presidential decision , \"","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"\" That authority is his ;","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"he can make the decisions .","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"I don ' t know","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"whether we were consulted or not ,","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"but whether we were or not ,","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"it ' s an executive decision for him","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"to make . \"","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"She pointed out","depth":6},{"id":152,"text":"that security clearances have traditionally been important tools for the U.S. intelligence community ,","depth":7},{"id":153,"text":"allowing agencies to rely the experiences of former department chiefs .","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"\" There ' s a whole range of people","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"that we rely on ,","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"including our formers","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"who have those clearances","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"to help us be better at what we do and know , \"","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"she said on the sidelines of a Defense Intelligence Agency conference in Omaha , Nebraska .","depth":6},{"id":160,"text":"Gordon said","depth":5},{"id":161,"text":"she didn ' t have any indication","depth":6},{"id":162,"text":"whether the removal of Brennan ' s clearances was part of a \" larger trend . \"","depth":6},{"id":163,"text":"She stressed , however ,","depth":6},{"id":164,"text":"that former agency leaders","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"- including those working for private companies and those still in government -","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"remain important parts of the intelligence community .","depth":7},{"id":167,"text":"And ,","depth":7},{"id":168,"text":"she said ,","depth":7},{"id":169,"text":"former officials with clearances should maintain certain standards","depth":7},{"id":170,"text":"to keep those clearances .","depth":7},{"id":171,"text":"Conservatives have over the past couple of weeks pushed for Brennan ' s security to be removed .","depth":6},{"id":172,"text":"Sen. Rand Paul","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"( R-Ky. )","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"in June said","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"he spoke to the president about that very issue ,","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"and Fox News host Tucker Carlson also called for Brennan ' s clearance to be removed","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"after he reported","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"he still had it .","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"On Wednesday , the Senate majority whip , John Cornyn","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"( R-Texas ) ,","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"who is on the Intelligence Committee ,","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"it was \" entirely appropriate \" for Trump to take action against Brennan .","depth":7},{"id":184,"text":"But Sen. Bob Corker","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"( R-Tenn. ) ,","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"the retiring chairman of the Foreign Relations Committee , said :","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"\" Without having some kind of tangible reasons","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"for doing so ,","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"which there may be","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"that I ' m not aware of ,","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"I don ' t like it at all .","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"It just feels like sort of a ... banana republic kind of thing , \"","depth":8},{"id":193,"text":"Brennan , in the MSNBC interview on Wednesday , said","depth":7},{"id":194,"text":"he believed","depth":8},{"id":195,"text":"that Trump was concerned about the criticism","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"Brennan has been voicing publicly","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"and was trying to diminish his integrity .","depth":9},{"id":198,"text":"\" I must tell you","depth":8},{"id":199,"text":"that Mr. Trump ' s dishonesty , his lack of integrity , his nastiness , mean-spiritedness , the types of things","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"that he has just tweeted out the past 72 hours ,","depth":11},{"id":201,"text":"the terms","depth":11},{"id":202,"text":"that he uses ,","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"this is not what I think of an American president , nor of America , \"","depth":9},{"id":204,"text":"Brennan said .","depth":7},{"id":205,"text":"\" We 're better than this .","depth":7},{"id":206,"text":"We have to be better than this .","depth":7},{"id":207,"text":"We have been a shining example to the world ,","depth":7},{"id":208,"text":"and Mr. Trump is letting this country down. \"","depth":7},{"id":209,"text":"In addition , Brennan criticized Trump ' s attacks on Mueller and his investigation .","depth":6},{"id":210,"text":"He added","depth":8},{"id":211,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":212,"text":"although he did not know any details from the inquiry ,","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"he believed","depth":11},{"id":214,"text":"that the president ' s recent attacks were a result of the \" closer magnification of some of the things","depth":13},{"id":215,"text":"that those around him have been involved in \"","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"through the probe .","depth":12},{"id":217,"text":"\" I know some things","depth":11},{"id":218,"text":"that the Russians were involved in ,","depth":11},{"id":219,"text":"but I certainly don ' t know all the things","depth":11},{"id":220,"text":"that Mr. Trump has been involved in over the years , \"","depth":11},{"id":221,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":222,"text":"\" I do not pretend to have that knowledge .","depth":10},{"id":223,"text":"He is the one .","depth":10},{"id":224,"text":"But clearly his actions are those of somebody","depth":10},{"id":225,"text":"who is seeking to prevent the full light of day being shone upon his past. \"","depth":10},{"id":226,"text":"Mueller ' s investigation should have a conclusion ,","depth":7},{"id":227,"text":"Brennan said ,","depth":7},{"id":228,"text":"and added","depth":8},{"id":229,"text":"that the American public should accept the findings no matter what .","depth":8},{"id":230,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"at the end of the day we all should accept the findings of that investigative team , \"","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":233,"text":"\" And","depth":9},{"id":234,"text":"if they exonerate everybody ,","depth":13},{"id":235,"text":"including Mr. Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":236,"text":"from any wrongdoing whatsoever ,","depth":12},{"id":237,"text":"we should accept that ,","depth":11},{"id":238,"text":"because that is what the rule of law demands","depth":11},{"id":239,"text":"and what our system of justice requires. \"","depth":11},{"id":240,"text":"John McLaughlin , a former acting director of the CIA ,","depth":8},{"id":241,"text":"who was not listed as having his clearance under review","depth":9},{"id":242,"text":"but has criticized the president 's policies in the past ,","depth":9},{"id":243,"text":"said on Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":244,"text":"that he thought","depth":7},{"id":245,"text":"the choice","depth":9},{"id":246,"text":"to revoke the clearance","depth":9},{"id":247,"text":"was to \" silence critics. \"","depth":8},{"id":248,"text":"\" This really has the feel of someone","depth":8},{"id":249,"text":"simply trying to do two things :","depth":9},{"id":250,"text":"silence critics","depth":10},{"id":251,"text":"and also distract from another damaging political event","depth":11},{"id":252,"text":"that ' s going on with Omarosa , \"","depth":11},{"id":253,"text":"he said during a phone interview on MSNBC ,","depth":7},{"id":254,"text":"referring to former presidential adviser Omarosa Manigault Newman ,","depth":7},{"id":255,"text":"whose new book includes scathing criticism of Trump and his administration .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":511,"left":392,"right":510,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":392,"left":354,"right":391,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":354,"left":311,"right":353,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":259,"right":310,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":0,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":257,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":257,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":274,"right":309,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":262,"right":273,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":4,"right":261,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":5,"right":260,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":260,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":268,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS